      *                              SRCFILE(&SL/&SF) +                     *
      *                              SRCMBR(&SM);                           *
      *                                                                     *
      *     >>COMPILE<<                                                     *
      *       >>PARM<< TRUNCNBR(*NO);                                       *
      *       >>PARM<< DBGVIEW(*LIST);                                      *
      *     >>END-COMPILE<<                                                 *
